---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Lashes & MGlamour">
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-8">
      <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl text-brand-pink font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        At **Lashes & MGlamour**, we respect your privacy. This policy outlines how we handle personal details collected during booking.
      </p>

      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-600 leading-relaxed">
        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-charcoal font-bold">1. Information Collection</h2>
        <p>
          We collect name, email, and phone coordinates solely to verify availability slots and secure reservations in the Square API systems.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-charcoal font-bold">2. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          Your details are encrypted and transmitted directly to Square. We do not store credit cards or payment details locally on our servers.
        </p>

        <h2 class="font-heading text-xl text-brand-charcoal font-bold">3. Third Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          We share booking details exclusively with Square to manage appointments, schedules, and SMS/Email verification links.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
